{"tid":3563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連尼住 LIHKG 成真正自由樂土，大家俾啲骨氣同支持！","createTime":"2016-11-26T07:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T08:53:40.000Z","uid":18179,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b5757444dd5f3e01bca51de797a024cb095ef6","tid":3563,"uid":18179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T07:45:32.000Z","msg":"連尼住 Facebook 5/7/2016<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人就認為寫個APP要賺錢係好正常既，當然賺錢既方式有好多種，我未用過HKG+，比唔到值唔值呢個價既評論，但我知以前iHKG都係收費既，間中都會限免。<br />\n<br />\n我唔明點解果時冇人會嘈，用家開心，賣家快樂，而家 D iFunDog一見到收錢就好似比人殺左老母咁<br />\n<br />\n我相信HKG+都同我一樣，本身都係想用廣告費，大財團既錢去營運隻APP，有獨立既Server去做Cache，比最好既服務大家。<br />\n<br />\n但當去到路得返兩條，一係就被Bam，一係就要收費，可以點做？LIHK係兩年半前就比Google下左架，AdSense都封埋，用一百蚊買我隻APP都Bam埋可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n想上返架，就係要同意Admin所訂立既Rule，賣APP，唔準落廣告，唔準事前Cache，只可以用API，當年百花齊放既Android高登APP，而家點解得返我一個係架？因為其他Developer都知，冇肉食。仲有DxtHKG，選擇無視規則地底生存。<br />\n<br />\n我原本係DC租左半隻櫃16粒IP做LIHK，當收到既錢唔夠養Server，營運唔到，個個月都要貼錢既，咪要Cut Server，將營運成本降低，用有限既資源做最好比大家。<br />\n<br />\n如果HKG+要繼續營運，要Keep住個獨立Server既，一定要收年費，如果唔係而家突然多出黎既錢唔頂得幾耐。<br />\n<br />\nIT人要食飯，當然有人要求回報係大既，有人就冇咩所謂，你認為值既咪買，唔值既，咪用開心版。<br />\n<br />\n#HKNOIT #IT人係狗係公廁 #IT狗你的資訊很有用 #IT狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家終於有機會俾大家離開高登<br />\n拜託俾啲骨氣，唔好做衰仔返去<br />\n同埋除咗口頭上支持外<br />\n亦都要俾返啲實際上嘅支持<br />\n連尼住請盡快提供VIP收費機制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34a26eb1c5d4e18cbae72ba0725f44ac8a1fc9e","tid":3563,"uid":11279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"Hkgolden 狗也不屌<br />\n支持lihkg 讚成收年費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fee609b1c4a41dd8d3745f52fe3272944193e2a","tid":3563,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T07:59:48.000Z","msg":"收年費一定科水<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cd94af74441a2bf73e6531335ad2c46d2a2e59","tid":3563,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"d6357b181de0799b536f50eec35433e3ba1038da","tid":3563,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:05:18.000Z","msg":"用一段時間睇下先 keep 住有正常人流當然要科水"},{"pid":"f74bea397445b6e5b8f4e5c9046972c835a08b80","tid":3563,"uid":18044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"好似hkg+咁 大家用開既 裝返呢個既應該都唔介意既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c07e2748d14beb5d7b3b15c798b7ef99a162ed","tid":3563,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:32:55.000Z","msg":"好用既野或服務<br />\n係應該要比錢<br />\n免費午餐唔係必然<br />\n美國好多IT公司有天使基金贊助<br />\n天使基金好多係來血矽谷早期成功既人<br />\n矽局文化係一代人幫下一代人<br />\n<br />\n香港得個數碼港(實際上係貝沙灣)同爛鬼創科局<br />\n所以要支持IT野搞得起搞得好<br />\n從民間集資係最正路<br />\n如果搞得唔好自然少人比錢支持會自然被淘汰<br />\n<br />\n其實搞第一個高登app既奧班馬都功不可抹<br />\niHKG同i2HKG都曾經係當時幾好既高登體驗<br />\n只係之後HKG+做得更好<br />\n<br />\n林早泄拎正牌靠高登年賺5百萬明明好有優勢<br />\n都唔投資多D錢去搞好高登論壇同個官方app<br />\n仲要打壓第三方app<br />\n就等於一個朝代既昏君打壓後起反抗之秀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n奧班馬、連尼住、Plus仔<br />\n都係覺得高登論壇唔夠好先要走出黎寫app<br />\n尋日大跳船我覺得已係成功改朝換代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以講係結集多位高登app developer同高登巴絲既心先做到<br />\n齊心就事成<br />\n<br />\n希望大家多D鼓勵識得既高登巴絲齊跳船<br />\n好簡單<br />\n只要Whatsapp同FB叫大家用LIHKG就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想睇林早泄見到高登人流下降<br />\n廣告商慢慢落少左廣告<br />\n最後後悔莫及既下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高登就好似TVB咁<br />\n做D野越黎越違背大量民意甚至與民為敵<br />\n依家連TVB都蝕錢要落廣告大特價<br />\n高登遲早都要落廣告減價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n水能載舟<br />\n亦能覆舟"},{"pid":"1bacb86379c804954a91a0cc7fba6e09bcdca549","tid":3563,"uid":16608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:35:36.000Z","msg":"點樣拒絕五毛，搞搞佢"},{"pid":"9bc9cf87332e3741887265c31141b1792efc53a3","tid":3563,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUZBpDs7wVTzLn3HYD9cCVS9bb6rsesj8m5g8fb6iSGpX?filename=WkxJwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWkxJwC.jpg&h=b82b1d38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/163937_57e426b05e7bd8266e08a6e9f50975a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F163937_57e426b05e7bd8266e08a6e9f50975a5.jpg&h=6d5ac6b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d084f60335f5e174e3a77cc3af9ca845ddedf3e","tid":3563,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣拒絕五毛，搞搞佢</blockquote><br />\n或者整個投訴機制<br />\n有得揀投訴原因<br />\n其中一個原因係五毛<br />\n如果同一個原因被投訴多過2百次<br />\n就被ban acc<br />\n我相信如果唔係真五毛<br />\n都好難比2百個人投訴係五毛<br />\n<br />\n同樣做法可以放落打手度<br />\n之前高登官方講過三星同Sony落得最多廣告<br />\n所以可以見到幾位三星打手長期無王管<br />\n但人地幾年前台灣mobile01三星打手都可以被揪出黎<br />\nLIHKG如想變樂土<br />\n真係應該減少D打手<br />\n一般打手純粹讚好某D野都算<br />\n有D職業煩膠打手真係個個新post都做假抹黑業界對手<br />\n完全係老千黎<br />\n<br />\n高登因為五毛、打手同大量小學雞<br />\nD post變得低質左好多<br />\n仲多左好多無謂既罵戰post<br />\n小學雞就唔應殺絕<br />\n因為小學雞都會成長變得成熟<br />\n五毛同打手收錢做野唔應該過份包容"},{"pid":"5cdfd0769fb36995ad61377c35a133c1d37758a0","tid":3563,"uid":18179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUZBpDs7wVTzLn3HYD9cCVS9bb6rsesj8m5g8fb6iSGpX?filename=WkxJwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWkxJwC.jpg&h=3ef0e1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/163937_57e426b05e7bd8266e08a6e9f50975a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F163937_57e426b05e7bd8266e08a6e9f50975a5.jpg&h=1f74e0d0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陳寶珊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}